---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Press Kit — Estate Sale Tales"
  description="Media resources for Estate Sale Tales. Author bio, book information, and contact details for press inquiries."
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container content-section">
      <p class="section-label">Press</p>
      <h1 class="section-title">Press Kit</h1>
      <p class="section-subtitle">
        Everything you need for coverage of <em>Estate Sale Tales</em>. For questions or interview requests, reach out directly.
      </p>

      <div class="press-content">
        <div class="press-block">
          <h2>About the Book</h2>
          <p>
            <em>Estate Sale Tales</em> is a collection of true stories from more than 20 years of estate liquidation. Spanning over 50 stories, the book captures the funny, bizarre, heartwarming, and downright unbelievable moments that come from clearing out 1,000+ homes. From snakes under beds to hidden fortunes in coat pockets, these are the stories that estate sale professionals swap after hours — now collected for the first time.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="press-block">
          <h2>Author Bio</h2>
          <p>
            Susan Callicott is the founder of Lucy & Ethel Estate Sales in the Dallas/Fort Worth, Texas area. She has spent over two decades in the estate liquidation industry, personally overseeing the clearing of more than 1,000 homes. What started as a practical career became an unexpected window into the lives, habits, and hidden stories of everyday people. <em>Estate Sale Tales</em> is her first book, with contributions from fellow professionals across the estate sale, auction, and cleanout industries.
          </p>
          <p class="bio-note">
            A shorter version for print: "Susan Callicott, founder of Lucy & Ethel Estate Sales in Dallas/Fort Worth, has cleared out over 1,000 homes in a 20-year career. <em>Estate Sale Tales</em> collects the true stories — funny, strange, and human — from that experience."
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="press-block">
          <h2>Book Cover</h2>
          <p>
            High-resolution book cover images are available for media use. Please contact us to receive the files.
          </p>
          <img src="/book-cover.jpg" alt="Estate Sale Tales book cover" style="width: 200px; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 0.75rem;" />
          <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 0.5rem;">
            <a href="/book-cover.jpg" download>Download high-res cover</a>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="press-block">
          <h2>Key Facts</h2>
          <ul class="facts-list">
            <li><strong>Title:</strong> Estate Sale Tales</li>
            <li><strong>Author:</strong> Susan Callicott</li>
            <li><strong>Genre:</strong> Humor / Nonfiction / Memoir</li>
            <li><strong>Stories:</strong> 50+</li>
            <li><strong>Rating:</strong> 4.8 out of 5 stars on Amazon</li>
            <li><strong>Formats:</strong> Paperback, Kindle ebook</li>
            <li><strong>Amazon:</strong> <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Estate-Sale-Tales-Susan-Callicott-ebook/dp/B0D2DPC1Y1/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">View on Amazon</a></li>
            <li><strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://estatesaletales.com">estatesaletales.com</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="press-block">
          <h2>Contact</h2>
          <p>
            For press inquiries, interview requests, or review copies:
          </p>
          <p>
            <a href="mailto:press@estatesaletales.com">press@estatesaletales.com</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .content-section {
    max-width: 680px;
  }
  .section-subtitle {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .press-content {
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }
  .press-block {
    padding: 2rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  }
  .press-block:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
  .press-block h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .press-block p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .bio-note {
    font-size: 0.9rem !important;
    font-style: italic;
    background: var(--bg-warm);
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }
  .facts-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .facts-list li {
    padding: 0.4rem 0;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }
  .facts-list li strong {
    color: var(--text);
  }
</style>
